item.title: Quickstart
item.description: The first step is to get an Ensign API key by visiting the sign-up page . Similar to getting a developer API key for Youtube , Twitter or Data.gov , you will need an API key to use Ensign and to follow along with the rest of this Quickstart guide. Ensign API Keys Your key consists of two parts, a ClientID and a ClientSecret. The ClientID uniquely identifies you, and the ClientSecret proves that you have permission to create and access event data.
